{"tid":340480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"父迫8歲女 5年間拍12套蘿莉AV","createTime":"2017-07-30T03:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T15:11:53.000Z","uid":25692,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32466083191c5a0028ac44f2223d383f627f3a9f","tid":340480,"uid":25692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T03:51:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/968529/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F968529%2F&d=Zz9ocIiwW4QtWCeezmK0mNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a2acfa8c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F968529%2F&h=d2c8bd8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/968529/</a><br />\n<br />\n日本兵庫縣一名47歲父親為了賺錢，強迫8歲親生女兒當色情片女優，直到近日才被揭發事件；女童在5年間已拍攝了12部的「蘿莉色情片」。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n女童現年13歲，她前年2月被迫以超小的透視泳裝拍了一部色情片，並在網絡上流傳；片段日前引起警方的關注，並將46歲的父親與「聖堂」影像公司社長、47歲男子秋元哲等三人拘捕。"},{"pid":"bcbb064940adb75c8e7afeb120ab96bd406504db","tid":340480,"uid":82532,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://s30.postimg.org/mjphab4dt/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs30.postimg.org%2Fmjphab4dt%2Fimage.jpg&h=640b6568&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b35c7892fdd8ecdbf192db33c9010913de11d5b8","tid":340480,"uid":17696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T04:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/https://s30.postimg.org/mjphab4dt/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs30.postimg.org%2Fmjphab4dt%2Fimage.jpg&h=640b6568&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bf3cfe9b58fc3c804d72c9019e3ff15c785b13","tid":340480,"uid":59078,"like":0,"dislik